rians alike.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aComposition (Music). 0aConducting. 0aErrata. 0aMusicxEditing. 0aOrchestral musicxAnalysis, appreciation. 0aOrchestral musicxHistory and criticism. 0aScore reading and playing. 4aMusic. 7aMUSIC / Genres & Styles / Classical.2bisacsh  aClassical Music.  aComposer.  aConducting Student.  aConductor.  aMusicologists.  aOrchestral Librarian.  aOrchestral Players.  aOrchestral Repertoire.  aReference Work.  aUrtext Edition.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBoydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311142849940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9781800106611?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781800106611423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781800106611/original  a978-3-11-142849-9  Boydell and Brewer Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  aGBV-deGruyter-alles